item.title: About
item.description: Hello! Welcome to the MooAI Group. We are graduate students in Computer Science from the University at Buffalo, State University of New York , with avid interest in Machine Learning and Deep Learning. This blog is a compilation of the our earlier work in the field of AI, allowing us to advance our knowledge in the domain. Cheers, MooAI Team
